lead_paragraph: Manager Aitor Karanka has hailed his Middlesbrough side for showing great character and spirit in the absence of skipper Grant Leadbitter and deputy George Friend.

headline.print_headline: Manager Karanka Lauds Boro Team Spirit Amid Injuries
